        </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h1 className="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Your Blog Title</h1>
        <p className="text-lg text-gray-700">
          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nulla quis lorem ut libero malesuada feugiat.
